nt":23,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"目前深圳龙岗区某公立小学编制，本硕 985➕部属师范。年薪税前 30w 左右。已经评过中一职称。想要去清北读博，再去国外拿双学位。 经济情况是三线城市普通家庭，父母已退休。深户未满 3 年，家里可以给出首付。有稳定的未婚夫，他已在深独立购房，待我满深户 3 年买房后立刻领证。以下说说理由： 1. 心里一直有个读博梦。硕士毕业匆忙找工作了，到底意难平。2. 博士学历对评副高有很大帮助。3. 相关专业博士毕业后也可以进入大学教马哲毛概。相比于中小学老师，更羡慕大学老师的生活。而且深圳大学给的工资和中小学差不多。4. 博士毕业回中小学也不抗拒。 担心： 1. 目前就业形势不好，读完博以后找不到目前水平的工作。2. 马上深户满可以购深房，三四年读博没有收入，又要还房贷。父母和自己会过的比较清简。3. 与未婚夫长期分居，怕或多或少影响感情。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I+fqr/OfksL0YEAMaCDYxNzM3MzY5IIOigoIGMBc43QdAHnIJNDQ3NTY0MzA4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"31_1629591694.006789","card_id":"Q_479196656","target":{"id":479196656,"title":"独居时你吃过最令人感动的食物是什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/479196656","type":"question","created":1628743178,"answer_count":151,"follower_count":1273,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[304,617,6311,106840,113183],"comment_count":3,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I+fqr/OfksL0YEAMaCDY4NzY5NDI2IIrM0ogGMAM4+QlAH3IJNDc5MTk2NjU2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-2add44e06fd9b258ffcbd3cd7447e33b_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"32_1629591694.0074158","card_id":"Q_28416669","target":{"id":28416669,"title":"有哪些适合在大学宿舍使用的椅子？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/28416669","type":"question","created":1425054084,"answer_count":102,"follower_count":1081,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2258,35460,68159,155458,548154],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"宿舍的原配凳子是个小木凳，坐着很不习惯。个人又比较喜欢在